# GitBoard File Uploads
# -----------------------
# By default, uploaded files in gitboard/uploads/ are tracked by git,
# which is consistent with GitBoard's file-system based architecture.
#
# If you prefer not to track uploaded binary files in git, uncomment the line below:
# gitboard/uploads/
#
# For large binary files, consider configuring Git LFS:
# https://git-lfs.github.com/
# Example .gitattributes:
#   gitboard/uploads/**/*.png filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
#   gitboard/uploads/**/*.jpg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
#   gitboard/uploads/**/*.pdf filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
.gitboard/app/node_modules/
.gitboard/
